---
description: CI quality/security gates
globs: [".github/workflows/**", ".pre-commit-config.yaml", "pyproject.toml", "requirements*.txt", "src/**", "tests/**"]
alwaysApply: true
---
- Quality gate: coverage ≥ 85.00%.
- Lint/format: ruff/black/isort must pass with 0 warnings.
- Security gate: bandit High=0; pip-audit --strict must pass.
- Pipeline target time: ≤ 5m (optimize if exceeded).
